    Is Gett more expensive than Uber?
    If UberX Surge Pricing Tops 1.7, Gett is Cheaper

    Generally speaking, if UberX surge pricing hits or exceeds 1.7X, you're better off using Gett to call a black cab for a fixed fare. During rush hour or a Friday or Saturday evening, it's not uncommon for Uber to charge 2X or more a normal fare.    Feb 25, 2018

    What does get a taxi mean?
    To get a taxi is to secure the services of a taxi for transportation. To take a taxi is to ride in one. That is, you have to get a taxi before you can take a taxi: You'll never get a taxi in this neighborhood/at this time of night/in this weather. We got a taxi at the airport and took it to the hotel.Jan 6, 2014

    Is gett taxi Israel?
    GetTaxi was founded by Israeli entrepreneurs Shahar Waiser and Roi More. In the summer of 2009, Waiser came up with the idea during a thirty-minute wait for a taxi to the airport in Palo Alto, California.
